Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/8/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the prolific Jose Alba Case, Ray J's latest goofiness, and much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
